{"tid":1680018,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"多次收到告白均拒絕！機師被灌醉「電梯深情連吻5下」再打包回家","createTime":"2019-10-28T14:13:37.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-29T04:55:52.000Z","uid":109923,"like":5,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"dd71215a94ea2a9f4312d12dfdc754e052d94670","tid":1680018,"uid":109923,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-28T14:13:37.000Z","msg":"中國南方航空公司近來被爆出性騷擾事件，旗下一名空少在電梯內緊緊抱著一名喝醉、無意識的男機師，連續親了對方臉頰5下，影片在網路上瘋狂流傳。據了解，兩人是南方航空（集團）深圳分公司員工，警方目前已介入調查。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/T8eEkj8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FT8eEkj8.jpg&h=97efdcdc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n根據《澎湃新聞》報導，男機師的朋友表示，事情發生在10日，兩人是同事關係，柴姓空少一直很喜歡機師，但多次在微信上告白但都被拒絕，那天柴男再度告白被拒心情不好，把自己講得很卑微，機師在同情之下才答應出去喝酒。<br />\n<br />\n機師朋友又透露，兩人喝完酒後，機師感覺到暈沉沉的，「感覺意識不是特別清楚，然後又走不動了，然後這個人（柴男）就把他帶回家裡了，然後就是有做出一些...」。機師朋友也指出，機師清醒後十分鬱悶，12日凌晨向派出所報案，並告知公司長官，但之後多次調解失敗。<br />\n<br />\n深圳南山派出所的民警表示，當事方和南航公司職員15日曾到派出所處協商，後來是自己回到公司協商。當時警方並未將事件列為「性騷擾」，但證實微信中曾出現「我喜歡你」等表白的字句。<br />\n<br />\n柴姓空少回應，影片是惡意截取，絕對沒有侵犯機師，在工作上已造成困擾，「我真的是被冤枉的」，目前已發律師函，之後就由派出所和法院公布事實真相。該律師函稱，「（飛行員）公開散佈虛假言論」、「逼迫下跪道歉」等。"},{"pid":"94316b059035b9c23eedb057f520fc3d3957ac55","tid":1680018,"uid":109923,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-28T14:14:05.000Z","msg":"《新京報》今（20日）的報導則宣稱取得更完整的畫面，影片中可見到，宣稱是男機師的白衣男子，跟穿著花襯衫的空少一邊談話、一邊走進電梯，不像喝醉的模樣，在電梯裡的親密舉止也不像是「失去意識」，疑為有心人先前刻意流傳剪接過的影片，找空少的麻煩。<br />\n<br />\n中國網友說：「白衣男子是碰瓷的吧」「建議黑衣男子告媒體。」（大陸中心／綜合外電報導）     <br />\n<br />\n影片 <a href=\"https://tw.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/20191020/1651375/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2F20191020%2F1651375%2F&d=SKXI%2FGePWbtdtN3kaacFP1CKRJWvDXkpEFRbHtszOvM%3D&h=2a8ee7d8\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2F20191020%2F1651375%2F&h=e9da1f5d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://tw.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/20191020/1651375/</a>"},{"pid":"636d4da88f67832c98ae76b38de9c93064250a24","tid":1680018,"uid":10195,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-28T14:15:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b11baca69af92f3be01d320a450310289cac9e90","tid":1680018,"uid":13421,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-28T14:16:46.000Z","msg":"好正<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1c7dd670e8551c82b1091317fbeb147e1b3c6216","tid":1680018,"uid":83602,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-28T14:17:22.000Z","msg":"扯左<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2560e458fe33b4329e2c4efb720f144da50c5567","tid":1680018,"uid":38904,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-28T14:17:57.000Z","msg":"多甜please<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3abdd7f644d7898511df0d865ae7e92cfabdc2f5","tid":1680018,"uid":204356,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-28T14:29:28.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">THIS</span></span>"},{"pid":"013e6421f3442a1ab04861baf3f934a6f8fcff85","tid":1680018,"uid":308618,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-28T14:33:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"11d0e3aa6d60dddebe4250f8f74a025dcccfb8e3","tid":1680018,"uid":16676,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-28T17:13:39.000Z","msg":"好温馨 <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/fX7eUFF.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FfX7eUFF.gif&h=478f0c09&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NkzMLNm.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNkzMLNm.gif&h=55e